Excellent! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile a comprehensive report of the design system component APIs.

## Design System Component APIs Report

Based on my analysis of `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/node_modules/@semparar/design-system-app/src`, here are the complete component APIs:

### 1. **Text**
**Location:** `atomic/atoms/Text`  
**Import:** `import { Text } from '@semparar/design-system-app'`

**Props Interface (TextPropsComponent):**
```typescript
{
  testID?: string;
  width?: string | number;
  maxWidth?: string | number;
  minWidth?: string | number;
  height?: string | number;
  children?: React.ReactNode[] | undefined | string | number;
  mt?: PropsSpacesHorizontal;  // margin-top
  ml?: PropsSpacesVertical;    // margin-left
  mb?: PropsSpacesHorizontal;  // margin-bottom
  mr?: PropsSpacesVertical;    // margin-right
  type?: PropsTokensTextCore;  // text style type
  lineThrough?: boolean;
  underline?: boolean;
  color?: PropsTokenColorsCore;
  align?: 'left' | 'center' | 'right';
  pd?: PropsPaddingCore;       // padding
  position?: 'relative' | 'absolute';
  numberOfLines?: number;
  allowFontScaling?: boolean;  // default: true
  maxFontSizeMultiplier?: number;
  accessibilityLabel?: string;
  colorLink?: PropsTokenColorsCore;      // color for links
  colorBold?: PropsTokenColorsCore;      // color for bold text
  colorHighlight?: PropsTokenColorsCore; // color for highlighted text
  index?: number;              // z-index
  disabled?: boolean;
  onPress?: (event?: string | GestureResponderEvent) => void;
  onLink?: (event?: string | GestureResponderEvent) => void;
}
```

---

### 2. **Button**
**Location:** `atomic/atoms/Button`  
**Import:** `import Button from '@semparar/design-system-app'` or named export `Button`

**Props Interface (PropsButton):**
```typescript
{
  mt?: PropsSpacesHorizontal;
  mb?: PropsSpacesHorizontal;
  ml?: PropsSpacesVertical;
  mr?: PropsSpacesVertical;
  testID?: string;
  width?: string | number;
  accessibility?: boolean;     // default: false
  type?: PropsTokensButtonCore; // e.g., 'primaryLarge', 'secundaryLarge', etc.
  text?: string;               // button label
  disabled?: boolean;
  contrast?: boolean;          // contrast mode
  icon?: PropsIconsNameCore;   // icon name
  isLoading?: boolean;
  onPress?: () => void;
}
```

